---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Itinerario from "../../components/Itinerario6d.astro";

const plan = {
  titulo: "Marvelous Cusco 6D/5N",
  imagen: "/bg-cusco-maravilloso-6d5n.avif",
};

const lang = "en";
---
<Layout>
    <section class="relative">
        <div class="relative h-[90vh] md:h-[80vh] rounded-b-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg" style={`background-image: url('${plan.imagen}'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;`}>

            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/70 via-black/60 to-black/70"></div>

            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center px-6">
                <h1 class="font-extrabold text-white drop-shadow-lg leading-tight text-[clamp(1.8rem,4vw,3.2rem)]">
                    {plan.titulo}
                </h1>
                <p class="mt-3 text-white/80 max-w-2xl text-[clamp(0.9rem,2vw,1.2rem)]">
                    Experience the magic of Cusco, the ancient capital of the Inca Empire, surrounded by history, culture, and unique landscapes.
                </p>

                <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 w-full sm:w-auto">
                    <a href="#itinerario" class="w-full sm:w-auto bg-green-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl shadow hover:bg-green-700 transition text-center">
                        See Itinerary
                    </a>
                    <a href={`https://wa.me/51973291892?text=${encodeURIComponent(`Hola, estoy interesado en reservar el paquete: ${plan.titulo}`)}`} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="w-full sm:w-auto bg-white/90 text-green-800 px-6 py-3 rounded-xl shadow hover:bg-white transition text-center">
                        Book now
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">

            <div class="bg-white shadow-xl rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-200">

                <div class="bg-green-700 text-white p-5">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Complete Panorama</h2>
                </div>

                <div class="p-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-4 text-justify">
                    <p>
                        We invite you to discover Cusco on a 6-day, 5-night tour, designed for travelers who want to experience the best of the ancient Inca Empire and be amazed by dreamy landscapes.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        During your stay, you'll explore ancient temples, streets steeped in history, and colorful Andean markets. You'll discover the Sacred Valley of the Incas, where tradition and spirituality live on among mountains and welcoming villages.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        ✨ And as the highlight, you'll experience the magic of Machu Picchu. You'll not only visit the citadel, but also tour its temples, terraces, and plazas, guided by experts who will reveal their secrets to you. You'll also have free time to admire this sacred site from its most impressive viewpoints, capturing memories that will last a lifetime.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        The adventure continues with two natural gems of Cusco: the Rainbow Mountain (Vinicunca) and the fascinating Humantay Lagoon, landscapes that seem straight out of a dream.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        This trip has it all: culture, nature, history, and unique moments that will make every day special.
